title: 'AI Propositions'
tags: ['AI', 'Propositions']
---

Author's note: In what follows, "AI" largely refers to Claude/ChatGPT-style LLMs and the associated agents.

1. The primary driving force behind AI development is not automation, efficiency, nor equity, but the movement of capital from the working class to the owning class. 

2. Atrophied _perspective taking_ from overreliance on AI is just as worrisome (if not moreso) than atrophied _critical thinking_.
